# Memory Bank Directory

This directory is intentionally empty.

The 8 core JSON files will be auto-generated when you run `/init`:
- activeContext.json
- scratchpad.json
- kanban.json
- mistakes.json
- systemPatterns.json
- progress.json
- roadmap.json
- memory.json

**Do not create these files manually.** The AI will generate them from schemas/ templates.
